title: Speed
position: -405,-22
---
TaxiDriver: Hey, I'm gonna speed it up a bit okay? I- I don't want you to be late... 
Pasajera: No no it's fine, I think we will get there in time
TaxiDriver: Right but i don't want you to be too late to your party. 
Pasajera: Oh believe me it's fine (she lowers her voice) It's not that much of a party anyways.
TaxiDriver: Look I'm gonna speed up just a tiny bit okay? There is practically noone at this hour.
Pasajera: I understand but even if most police officers are not on duty right not, the radars don't celebrate new years.
Pasajera: Seriously thank you but, we are not that far away don't worry about it. I woudn't want you to get in trouble
TaxiDriver: Yeah alright i'll just go easy then, sorry I just don't want you going late. I don't want you to miss such an important date...
<<jump Silence>>
